You should have received a copy of the GNU General Public License along with this program; if not, write to the Free Software Foundation, Inc., 59 Temple Place, Suite 330, Boston, MA 02111-1307 USA The template is used by the WmlDeckBuilder to capture the events specified in the <template> element, and assign these to the deck. Once an object of this class has been created it is treated by the WmlDeckBuilder as any other card, however internally it simply passes the relevant contained items to the WmlDeck to deal with.
